member.summary:
This class is used to parse string data for both XmlNode and XmlDocument data.
Parameter: string custom - contains an XPath query imbeded within a string value. The XPath will be contained in Triple brackets. {{{XPath}}} For Example: {{{ XPath }}} string
{{{//Profile/@EntityName}}} | Harvard Catalyst Concepts ({{{//Profile/NetworkList/Network[@RelationshipType="Researches"]/@FullCount}}})
Parameter: XmlNode/XmlDocument - cotains xml based data used to apply to the custom XPath parameter. XmlNode is part of a Network or Connection list loop call, XmlDocument will be used as part of a Profile data set but is not restricted to just Profile data.
